from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier

# K
neighbors = [1,3,5,7,9]
# 
knn_acc=[]
# TODO
# neighborsKKNeighborsClassifier
# Kknn_acc
for k in neighbors:
    knn = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=k)
    knn.fit(X_train,y_train)
    accuracy = knn.score(X_test,y_test)
    print("n:{} {}".format(k,accuracy))
    knn_acc.append(accuracy)

results_df = pd.DataFrame(columns=['Accuracy (%)'],index=['svm','dt','gnb','knn','lr'])
results_df.index.name = 'Model'
results_df.loc['svm', 'Accuracy (%)'] = max(svm_acc) * 100
results_df.loc['dt', 'Accuracy (%)'] = max(dt_acc) * 100
results_df.loc['gnb', 'Accuracy (%)'] = max(gnb_acc) * 100
results_df.loc['knn', 'Accuracy (%)'] = max(knn_acc) * 100
results_df.loc['lr', 'Accuracy (%)'] = max(lr_acc) * 100

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))
ax1 = plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
results_df.plot(y=['Accuracy (%)'], kind='bar', ylim=[70, 100], ax=ax1, title='Accuracy(%)', legend=False)


plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

In [75]:
from sklearn.metrics import f1_score
# TODO
# F1dataframeresults_df
results_df = pd.DataFrame(columns=['f1'],index=['svm','dt','gnb','knn','lr'])
results_df.index.name = 'Model'

dt = DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=depths[dt_acc.index(max(dt_acc))])
dt.fit(X_train,y_train)

knn = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=neighbors[knn_acc.index(max(knn_acc))])
knn.fit(X_train,y_train)

f1_score_ls = []
models = [svc,dt,gnb,knn,lr]
for model in models:
    f1_score_ls.append(f1_score(y_test,model.predict(X_test),average='macro')*100)

print(f1_score_ls)
results_df['f1'] = f1_score_ls

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))
ax1 = plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
results_df.plot(y=['f1'], kind='bar', ylim=[0, 100], ax=ax1, title='F1 score(%)', legend=False)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
